subSubSection.paragraph:
Descriptive notes.
Head-body 23-29 cm, tail 30-33 cm; weight 1.1-1 kg. The Southern Woolly Lemuris similar in size to the Eastern Woolly Lemur (A. 
laniger
) and Peyrieras’s Woolly Lemur (A. 
peyrierasi
). The dorsal furis gray-brown, toning down to light gray distally, and the ventrum is gray. The tail is red-brown and darkens distally.
